|               |                             |              |                                                                                        |
| Array/Struct  |                             |              | After user array partition and struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas are applied       |
|               | (1) array partition         | 2,610        | user array partition pragmas are applied                                               |
|               | (2) simplification          | 2,406        | simplification of applied user array partition & struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas |
|               | (3) aggregate/disaggregate  | 2,455        | user struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas are applied                                 |
|               | (4) array reshape           | 3,801        | apply array reshape pragmas                                                            |
|               | (5) access patterns         | 3,951        | array access pattern optmizations                                                      |
|               |                             |              |                                                                                        |
| Performance   |                             |              | After transformations are applied to meet performance pragma targets                   |
|               | (1) loop simplification     | 3,908        | loop and instruction simplification                                                    |
|               | (2) parallelization         | 3,765        | loops are unrolled or pipelined to meet performance targets                            |
|               | (3) array partition         | 3,402        | arrays are partitioned to meet performance targets                                     |
|               | (4) simplification          | 3,402        | simplification of design after performance transformations                             |
|               |                             |              |                                                                                        |
| HW Transforms |                             |              | After hardware transfomations                                                          |
|               | (1) lowering                | 3,068        | initial conversion to HW specific instructions                                         |
|               | (2) optimizations           | 3,221        | high level synthesis optimizations                                                     |
